Interactive Shiny Application

The dashboard allows users to filter the Q2 visualization by treatment arm 
interactively. All three arms are selected by default, and the chart updates 
dynamically as selections change — including recalculating the SOC ordering 
to reflect only the currently visible data.

Notes:
- Data loading and preparation is done outside the server for efficiency, 
  so heavy processing only happens once at app startup.
- The severity colour scale (light to dark) and ordering (MILD → MODERATE → SEVERE) 
  are consistent with Q2 for a cohesive presentation.
- A guard is in place to prevent the chart from erroring when all treatment 
  arms are deselected.

Live app: https://choqyy-april-cheng.shinyapps.io/RVA-Q3-Shiny
